Market Segmentation: 
The walking assist devices market is segmented on the basis of product type and distribution channel. The growth amongst these segments will help you analyse meagre growth segments in the industries, and provide the users with valuable market overview and market insights to help them in making strategic decisions for identification of core market applications. 
Based on the product type, the walking assist devices market is segmented into gait belts and lift vests, canes, crutches, walker, wheelchairs, and power scooters. Canes is further sub segmented into quad canes and folding canes. Walker is further sub segmented into standard walkers, rolling walkers and rollators and hemi walkers. Wheelchairs is further sub segmented into manual wheelchairs and electric wheelchairs. Electric wheelchairs is further sub segmented into front wheel drive, center wheel drive, rear wheel drive and standing power wheelchairs. Power scooters is further sub segmented into boot scooters, road scooters and pavement scooters.
Based on the distribution channel, the walking assist devices market is segmented into online, and offline.
